reviewText: Great selection, we enjoyed the Spanish track

This is the Spanish version, God of Wonders, showing the beauty and awesomeness of the earth, the plant, and the animal life created by God. The ending ties everything together, encouraging us to know the God of power who loves us and wants us to know Him.  Christians and non-Christians alike will be thrilled watching this DVD.
Muy buen video, nos muestra claramente las maravillas de Dios y como por su complejidad no hay lugar a dudas de Su existencia.
If, you belive in Jesus the lord you have to see.  This video Jhon 3:16  God love you and he live forever.
